  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: What did you see?
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: A Grove Of Fluffy Bunnies...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Then that is where the end of the universe begins.


      Search
      the area and try to find someone to help you.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Bunnies Destroy The Universe?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Saving the universe sounds like a job that will require a great
      deal of assitance.
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Against Fluffy Bunnies?!!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'I have placed a time crystal up those stairs near the top of pyramid
      above you.


      It is linked to the location in space and time you saw.


      Touch
      the crystal and it will teleport you to the grove.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: Hah, bunnies... I got this!
